Detailed Description

cvmx_dfm_fnt_sclk

DFM_FNT_SCLK = DFM Front SCLK Control Register

This register contains control registers for the DFM Front Section of Logic. NOTE: This register is in USCLK domain and is ised to enable the conditional SCLK grid, as well as to start a software BiST sequence for the DFM sub-block. (note: the DFM has conditional clocks which prevent BiST to run under reset automatically).
